THE STORY

ANAH LE NOM is the real Shiba Inu behind the iconic $SHIB token.

OG $SHIB holders have now turned their attention to $ANAH

In 2012, the owner of Doge, @kabosumama, was in contact with Hana's owner, @Hana_Papa_, marking the start of a connection between two iconic dogs.

The historic $SHIB logo was inspired by Hana's Instagram, and both the $SHIB and $ANAH logos were created by the legendary @ParadoxDesigner, making them a part of crypto history.

Discover Hana’s story and join her journey before the rest of the world does!
